  "id": "RAW_6c82b61b",
  "title": "AI 生成乡村歌曲登顶 Billboard 榜首：这该让所有人愤怒",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247620617&idx=2&sn=1d5513a6599bfd17846242b4b854a35e",
  "date": "2025-11-17 03:03:00",
  "author": "硅星人Pro",
  "siteName": "硅星人Pro",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 30px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;background:none;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100136959\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bb8af29&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBLc3tpKVSWyoxyx6beiaibiaLByR4mTJ301ZSoqKwtmz93vXG46FNMITju8HD30Vp4VpHQULshT9miaeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近在浏览海外音乐媒体时，我注意到一个重磅消息在乡村音乐圈引发轩然大波。美国乡村音乐文化媒体Whiskey Riff发布了一篇措辞严厉的文章，标题直指\"一首AI生成的乡村歌曲正在霸占Billboard榜单，这应该让我们所有人愤怒\"。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去一年，AI音乐工具如Suno、Udio的爆火让AI创作音乐从实验室走向大众，但这些作品大多停留在社交媒体传播的层面。而这次不同的是，</span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">一首完全由AI生成的歌曲，首次登上了Billboard官方榜单的第一名</span></b><span leaf=\"\">。这不再是技术演示或小圈子的新奇玩具，而是实打实地进入了主流音乐产业的核心评价体系。这个事件标志着AI音乐已经从\"能做\"进入到\"在做\"，甚至\"做得比真人还成功\"的新阶段。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi2fb2xckid\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi2fb2xh1mz6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">完整歌曲纯享，还怪好听</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个不存在的歌手，登上了真实的榜单</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">本周Billboard乡村数字单曲销售榜的冠军，是一首名为《Walk My Walk》的歌曲，演唱者叫\"Breaking Rust\"。如果你从未听说过这个名字，那很正常——因为这个\"歌手\"根本不存在，它是一个完全由AI生成的虚拟项目。</span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100136954\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45466666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"860\" style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;\" width=\"1894\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e054088d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBLc3tpKVSWyoxyx6beiaibiaLBGsutDN5HwBeGfHLAfK76vgEbGpnOUCJw2BbibsAHxFBiaNfq88EHFNiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这首歌署名为Aubierre Rivaldo Taylor，此人同时还运营着另一个AI音乐账号\"Defbeatsai\"。有趣的是，Defbeatsai的社交媒体上明确标注了\"AI生成\"的身份，但Breaking Rust的Instagram个人简介里只写着\"亡命乡村\"和\"我们的灵魂音乐\"，对AI身份只字未提。Billboard在报道其他AI艺术家登榜时，证实了Breaking Rust确实是AI生成项目。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种选择性的透明度引发了质疑：是技术展示，还是刻意隐瞒？</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">数字背后的荒诞</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Breaking Rust自10月15日注册Instagram以来，迅速积累了超过3万粉丝，但翻看评论区和粉丝列表，大量账号表现出明显的机器人特征。更惊人的是，它在Spotify上的月度听众数达到了</span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">180万</span></b><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100136955\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.528\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"766\" style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;\" width=\"1450\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f86248cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBLc3tpKVSWyoxyx6beiaibiaLBo6AVzATD1lmP8c4KtmEBvQ1jiap1nT1mudxoJpI0iaPzVzHlVWxIh0Rg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个数字意味着什么？作为对比，刚刚发布新专辑的真人乡村歌手Colby Acuff，月度听众刚过100万；以高产著称的独立音乐人Charley Crockett，月度听众也只有140万。一个刚出现不到一个月、连真人都不是的\"歌手\"，流量超过了这些在舞台上摸爬滚打多年的艺术家。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这次榜单上，真人歌手Ella Langley的新单曲《Choosin’ Texas》位列第二。换句话说，如果没有这首AI歌曲，她本该拿下冠军。这不是假设性的损失，而是真金白银的曝光机会和收入被一个算法挤掉了。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Billboard的沉默与产业的默许</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Whiskey Riff的作者联系了Billboard，询问他们对AI歌曲上榜有什么政策规定，是否会将AI作品与真人创作区分标注，但截至发稿没有收到回复。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">根据Billboard自己的统计，过去几个月至少有6位\"AI或AI辅助艺术家\"出现在各类榜单上，而他们也承认，实际数字可能更高，因为现在的AI音乐已经很难被识别出来。从目前的报道口径看，Billboard似乎并不认为这是个需要\"解决\"的问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种态度背后折射的是整个产业链的默许。流媒体平台Spotify只关心播放量，不管播放的是谁的作品，反正都能赚钱。唱片公司虽然现在还没公开表态，但按商业逻辑推演，未来推出自己的AI\"艺术家\"只是时间问题——它不需要签约、不需要巡演、不会闹解约，还能7×24小时产出内容。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者在文章里提到一个细节：一年前他写过一篇关于AI艺术家在Spotify上传翻唱歌曲的文章，结果收到了律师函要求撤稿。他没有撤，现在看来，当时的争议只是个开始。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是EDM，也不是\"工具进化\"</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">可能有人会说，电子音乐（EDM）不也是用电脑做的吗？为什么AI音乐就不行？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章对此做了区分：EDM确实大量使用电脑和软件，但制作过程依然需要真人艺术家投入才华、审美和创作精力去混音、编曲、设计声音。那是人借助工具完成的创作。而AI音乐是直接输入指令，让算法吐出成品，中间没有任何人类的艺术劳动参与。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是工具的进化，而是创作主体的替换。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">田纳西州的立法与法律的空白</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年早些时候，田纳西州通过了法律，禁止未经授权使用AI\"深度伪造\"他人的声音。这针对的是那些用AI模仿Taylor Swift、Morgan Wallen等明星声音的作品，保护的是已有艺术家的权益。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但对于像Breaking Rust这样\"原创\"的AI音乐，法律几乎没有设置任何门槛。它不侵犯任何人的肖像权或版权，所以可以畅通无阻地上传、发行、登榜。这个法律真空意味着，未来这类内容只会越来越多。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">谁在受益，谁在受伤</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个故事里，平台、资本、算法都是赢家。Spotify继续收流量费，Billboard继续卖榜单关注度，AI工具公司继续卖订阅。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正受损的是两类人：</span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">创作音乐的艺术家</span></b><span leaf=\"\">和</span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">消费音乐的听众</span></b><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">艺术家发现，自己花几个月甚至几年打磨的作品，市场表现可能不如一个算法花几分钟生成的东西。这不是因为作品不好，而是因为算法可以更快、更便宜、更批量地占据注意力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">听众则在不知不觉中，被喂食越来越多空洞、公式化、毫无灵魂的内容。Breaking Rust的歌听起来\"还行\"，但仔细品味会发现歌词乏味、旋律套路、编曲平庸。它的成功不是因为艺术价值，而是因为算法优化和流量操控。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当这样的内容开始占据榜单、占据推荐位、占据听众的耳朵，真正有深度的音乐会越来越难被听见。</span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100136956\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"1024\" style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;\" width=\"1536\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ab72946a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBLc3tpKVSWyoxyx6beiaibiaLBSIRPzNjfoqSXLmOljBydPTn3ZStfzNwF21hzFqsqq6W8ZJ2eJ6WX2g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们正在接近的临界点</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Whiskey Riff的作者用了\"point of no return\"（无法回头的临界点）这个词。他担心的是，当产业链的每个环节都默许甚至鼓励AI内容时，这个趋势会自我强化，直到真人创作彻底失去竞争力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是科幻小说里的远景，而是正在发生的现实。一个AI\"歌手\"已经拿到了Billboard冠军，下一步会是什么？AI专辑横扫年度榜单？格莱美奖出现AI提名？音乐节舞台上播放AI的\"现场\"？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章的标题说\"这应该让我们所有人愤怒\"，但更现实的问题可能是：当愤怒无法改变商业逻辑时，我们还能做什么？</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "一首 AI 生成的乡村歌曲登顶 Billboard 榜单，引发了对 AI 音乐对传统音乐产业、艺术家和听众影响的深刻担忧。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "一首 AI 生成的乡村歌曲登顶 Billboard 榜单，引发了对 AI 音乐对传统音乐产业、艺术家和听众影响的深刻担忧。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了一首完全由 AI 生成的乡村歌曲《Walk My Walk》登顶 Billboard 数字单曲销售榜的事件，指出这标志着 AI 音乐已从技术演示走向主流成功。作者揭示了 AI 虚拟歌手“Breaking Rust”在社交媒体和流媒体平台上的流量可能存在操控，并对比真人歌手的听众数据，凸显了 AI 对真人艺术家曝光和收入的挤占。文章批评 Billboard 和流媒体平台对 AI 音乐的默许态度，以及现有法律在“原创”AI 音乐方面的空白，预示着 AI 内容将进一步泛滥。文章强调 AI 音乐并非工具进化，而是创作主体替换，其批量化、公式化的内容可能损害音乐艺术的深度和听众体验，并对行业未来走向表示担忧。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 生成的歌曲首次登顶主流榜单，标志着 AI 音乐从“能做”到“成功”的新阶段。",
      "explanation": "过去 AI 音乐多停留在社交媒体传播层面，此次登上 Billboard 榜首，显示 AI 已进入主流评价体系，对传统音乐产业构成直接挑战。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 歌曲通过不透明操作和流量操控，挤占真人艺术家的市场空间和收入。",
      "explanation": "虚拟 AI 歌手通过机器人粉丝和异常高的播放量，超越真人艺术家，导致真人作品曝光和收入受损，反映市场竞争的不公平性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "音乐产业（Billboard、流媒体平台）对 AI 音乐的默许以及法律空白，将加速 AI 内容的普及。",
      "explanation": "榜单机构和平台缺乏明确政策，现有法律对“原创”AI 音乐无限制，使得 AI 内容可无阻碍地发行和登榜，加剧对真人创作的冲击。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 音乐并非“工具进化”，而是“创作主体替换”，其批量化、公式化内容可能损害音乐艺术的深度和听众体验。",
      "explanation": "AI 音乐是算法直接生成，缺乏人类艺术劳动，与 EDM 不同。其成功源于算法优化而非艺术价值，长此以往将导致市场充斥空洞内容。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "一首完全由 AI 生成的歌曲，首次登上了 Billboard 官方榜单的第一名。",
    "这不是工具的进化，而是创作主体的替换。",
    "但对于像 Breaking Rust 这样'原创'的 AI 音乐，法律几乎没有设置任何门槛。",
    "当这样的内容开始占据榜单、占据推荐位、占据听众的耳朵，真正有深度的音乐会越来越难被听见。",
    "文章的标题说'这应该让我们所有人愤怒'，但更现实的问题可能是：当愤怒无法改变商业逻辑时，我们还能做什么？"
